      Variance can be calculated using different formulas depending on whet=
her the data being analyzed is from a <span data-v-6b5e7006=3D"" class=3D"b=
olded-texts">population</span> or a <span data-v-6b5e7006=3D"" class=3D"bol=
ded-texts">sample</span>.
    </p> <p data-v-6b5e7006=3D"" class=3D"bottom-margins">
